MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

Parker v. Protective Life Ins. Co. of Ohio.

Trumbull App. Nos. 2004-T-0127 and 2004^-T-0128, 2006-0hio-4041. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
